<figureCitation box="[926,1007,1277,1303]" captionStart="FIGURE 4" captionStartId="8.[136,229,1991,2013]" captionTargetBox="[166,1422,191,1966]" captionTargetId="figure-22@8.[165,1422,190,1966]" captionTargetPageId="8" captionText="FIGURE 4. Species of Fabaceae Lindl. of the study area, Pico do Jabre State Park, Paraíba, Brazil. a Chamaecrista nictitans. b Anadenanthera colubrina. c Chamaecrista zygophylloides. d Albizia polycephala. e Senna macranthera. f Mimosa invisa. g Senna rizzinii. h Calliandra subspicata. i Enterolobium contortisiliquum. j Senna martiana. (Source: the authors)." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6875649" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6875649/files/figure.png" pageId="5" pageNumber="22">Fig. 4b</figureCitation>
